RIYADH: Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman received a message from Mahamat Idriss Deby Itno, chairman of the Transitional Military Council of Chad, regarding relations between the two countries, the Saudi Press Agency reported on Sunday. This came during a meeting between Saudi Foreign Affairs Minister Faisal bin Farhan bin Abdullah and his Chadian counterpart Mahamat Saleh Annadif. During the meeting, they discussed bilateral relations, opportunities for cooperation in various fields, and regional and international issues of mutual concern.